text: Kepong Baru ({}) is a suburb in Kepong, Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia. It is located between Bandar Menjalara, Taman Usahawan and Segambut. There will be one metro station at Kepong Baru after 2021, named Kepong Baru station.https://www.thestar.com.my/metro/community/2015/11/14/kepong-baru- revisited-not-much-has-changed-in-kls-sleepy-suburb-despite-surrounding- development ==References== Category:Suburbs in Kuala Lumpur
